genresAdvancedInfo.name: rock pernambucano
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Originating from the state of Pernambuco, Brazil, this genre of rock music has a unique sound that blends traditional northeastern Brazilian rhythms with rock. The lyrics often focus on social and political issues, reflecting the state's history of activism. Bands like Nação Zumbi and Mundo Livre S/A are popular representatives of this genre.
